**: This code is an __init__.py file for a Python package. It imports the FinanceAnalyzer class from a submodule named analyzer and adds it to the __all__ list. The __all__ variable specifies which names are imported when a user does a wildcard import (e.g., from package import *). Its purpose is to expose the FinanceAnalyzer class as part of the package's public API, allowing easy access to it without needing to import the submodule directly.

